sulation effectiveness";s:4:"slug";s:36:"garage-door-insulation-effectiveness";s:5:"title";s:55:"The Best Garage Door Insulation Kits Garage Door Nation";s:3:"alt";s:18:"garage door nation";s:3:"url";s:106:"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0176/1636/articles/The_Best_Garage_Door_Insulation_Kits.png?v=1597774742";s:5:"thumb";s:90:"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcROBIjsv8NJ5N62uzYr2OR7BMZWHbooKzpqEA";s:8:"filetype";s:3:"jpg";s:5:"width";i:1080;s:6:"height";i:1080;s:6:"source";s:76:"https://www.garagedoornation.com/blogs/home/best-garage-door-insulation-kits";s:6:"domain";s:24:"www.garagedoornation.com";}}s:9:"sentences";a:63:{i:0;s:76:"However the exact level of effectiveness depends on a few factors including.";i:1;s:24:"The climate you live in.";i:2;s:62:"Insulation is more effective in some environments than others.";i:3;s:24:"For example frigid cold.";i:4;s:23:"The type of insulation.";i:5;s:75:"Both polystyrene and polyurethane insulation work well but polyurethane is.";i:6;s:22:"Spray foam insulation.";i:7;s:64:"Sprayed onto your garage door but not the most effective method.";i:8;s:120:"The same kind of insulation sometimes sprayed against roof sheathing from the inside to improve the R-value in an attic.";i:9;s:33:"Must be sprayed onto garage door.";i:10;s:79:"Provides much better results than spray foam but its the most expensive option.";i:11;s:87:"An insulated garage door to the interior of the house will help lower your energy bill.";i:12;s:102:"Use your thermal leak detector on conduits such as electrical outlets and openings for pipes or wires.";i:13;s:94:"To insulate outlets look for socket sealers wall plate insulation or electrical socket covers.";i:14;s:81:"Garage door insulation It does help to keel the garage cool with insulated doors.";i:15;s:49:"The slab if it uninsulated also helps on cooling.";i:16;s:70:"I have foam filled doors with metal on both side so no flaking either.";i:17;s:51:"Ground temperature here is about 50-